State machine triggers recordings on bridge (verified by TestRecordingStartOnBridge), stops recordings before finalization, publishes recording merge for bridged calls (verified by TestRecordingMergePublishOnFinalize), fires webhooks on all 7 status transitions (verified by TestWebhookPublishOnEachStatusChange), errors are non-blocking (verified by TestRecordingErrorDoesNotAbortCall and TestWebhookErrorDoesNotAbortTransition)

